headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: Global Business Travel (NYSE:GBTG) And The Rest Of The Finance and HR Software Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at finance and hr software stocks, starting with Global Business Travel (NYSE:GBTG).
